      <title>菲律宾农业部长希望缩短大米关税削减期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/philippines-agriculture-chief-wants-rice-tariff-cut-shortened</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾是全球最大的大米购买国之一，农业部长弗朗西斯科·蒂乌·劳雷尔 (Francisco Tiu Laurel) 表示，该国应最多将大米进口关税下调一年，而不是下调至 2028 年，以限制对农民的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/philippines-agriculture-chief-wants-rice-tariff-cut-shortened</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 10:28:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长 Centeno 表示，若通胀放缓，利率可能进一步下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/ecb-s-centeno-says-rates-can-be-cut-further-if-inflation-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员马里奥·森特诺表示，只要通胀继续缓和，欧洲央行就可以进一步放松货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/ecb-s-centeno-says-rates-can-be-cut-further-if-inflation-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 10:13:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国利差扩大，一年后损失 8 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/france-sees-wider-spreads-costing-800-million-after-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部估计，总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙宣布提前举行立法选举后，法国债务遭到抛售，如果高额借贷成本持续一年，法国将蒙受约 8 亿欧元（8.59 亿美元）的额外损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/france-sees-wider-spreads-costing-800-million-after-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 10:10:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞的政党支持武装乌克兰，称“不会派遣法国军队”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/le-pen-s-party-backs-arming-ukraine-says-no-french-troops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞所在国民联盟党主席乔丹·巴德拉表示，他赞成向乌克兰提供自卫所需的弹药，但不会提供可能引发更大规模战争的装备，这与法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙在法国在冲突中的作用上的立场相对接近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/le-pen-s-party-backs-arming-ukraine-says-no-french-troops</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 10:09:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威首次降息可能还要半年：决策指南</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/norway-central-bank-first-interest-rate-cut-is-likely-half-a-year-away</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威央行可能即将发出信号，表明在经济显示出基本能够承受紧缩货币政策的迹象的情况下，央行还远未准备好削减借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/norway-central-bank-first-interest-rate-cut-is-likely-half-a-year-away</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西央行因信誉危机暂停降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/brazil-central-bank-is-set-to-halt-interest-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政策制定者面临全面的信誉危机，且难以抑制进一步超出目标的通胀预期，巴西央行可能会暂停近一年的降息周期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/brazil-central-bank-is-set-to-halt-interest-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场关注法国和意大利因赤字问题受到欧盟谴责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/france-and-italy-get-eu-scolding-for-deficits-as-markets-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国和意大利因巨额赤字而受到欧盟的谴责，这是对抗的第一阶段，将考验欧盟的决心，理论上可能引发数十亿欧元的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/france-and-italy-get-eu-scolding-for-deficits-as-markets-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 09:37:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员加大对南非通胀放缓至目标的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/traders-boost-bets-on-south-african-inflation-slowing-to-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们越来越多地押注南非通胀将放缓至该国央行目标区间的中点，这将为政策制定者在第四季度转向宽松周期提供空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/traders-boost-bets-on-south-african-inflation-slowing-to-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 06:34:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市难以在美国科技股上涨中继续领涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员在美国最新科技股推动的上涨之后寻找新的催化剂，欧洲股市难以延续两天的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 22:36:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奢侈运动鞋制造商 Golden Goose 推迟计划 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/permira-backed-golden-goose-is-said-to-postpone-planned-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于奢侈品股遭遇抛售，且欧洲政治风险再度升温，市场对这家由 Permira 支持的运动鞋公司的兴趣有所减弱，Golden Goose Group SpA 最终取消了在米兰的上市计划，尽管该公司已经下调了估值预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/permira-backed-golden-goose-is-said-to-postpone-planned-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 20:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
